        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-section">
            <div class="about-content">
                <h2>About CodeSphere</h2>
                <p>CodeSphere is an innovative interactive learning platform designed to help you master data structures and algorithms (DSA) and enhance your coding skills through hands-on practice. Our mission is to make coding education accessible, engaging, and effective for everyone.</p>
                <p>With our user-friendly interface, comprehensive exercises, and built-in coding IDE, we provide the perfect environment for learning at your own pace. Whether you're a beginner looking to learn programming fundamentals or an experienced developer preparing for technical interviews, CodeSphere has the tools you need to succeed.</p>
                <p>Our platform combines the best of interactive learning with real-world coding challenges, giving you the opportunity to apply what you learn immediately. The integrated development environment allows you to write, test, and debug code without ever leaving the platform.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80" alt="Coding on laptop">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Built-in IDE</h3>
                <p>Practice coding directly in our powerful web-based IDE with syntax highlighting, auto-completion, and real-time error checking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>DSA Learning</h3>
                <p>Master data structures and algorithms with our structured curriculum, visualizations, and interactive challenges.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-language"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Multiple Languages</h3>
                <p>Learn in your preferred language with support for Python, Java, C++, JavaScript, and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                </div>
