                <p>Monitor your learning journey with detailed analytics and personalized recommendations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Supports multiple programming languages including Python, Java, C++, and JavaScript</li>
                <li>Interactive problem-solving environment with immediate feedback</li>
