        <div class="advantages">
            <h2>Why Choose CodeSphere?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Improve coding proficiency with targeted exercises tailored to your skill level</li>
                <li>Access up-to-date learning resources curated by industry experts</li>
                <li>Prepare effectively for technical interviews with mock coding tests</li>
                <li>Track your learning progress in real-time with comprehensive dashboards</li>
                <li>Join a community of passionate developers to collaborate and learn together</li>
                <li>Learn at your own pace with flexible course structures</li>
                <li>Get certificate upon completion of learning paths</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cta">
            <p>Start your journey with CodeSphere today and become a proficient developer.</p>
            <button onclick="location.href='/index'">Join CodeSphere Now</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
        <div class="contact-container">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
            <div class="contact-icons">
                <a href="mailto:contact@codesphere.com" class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
                <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i></a>
                <a href="https://maps.google.com" class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i></a>
